{{der-top|Idioms}}
* {{ja-r|百に一つ|ひゃく に ひとつ}}: “one in a hundred” → something [[rare]] or [[unusual]]
* {{ja-r|百も承%知|ひゃく も しょう%ち}}: “awareness of the hundred” → the state of being [[fully]] [[aware]] of something
{{der-bottom}}

{{der-top}}
* {{ja-r|百%科 全書|ひゃっ%か ぜんしょ}}: an [[encyclopedia]]
* {{ja-r|百%千|ひゃく%せん}}: a large number, all sorts, hundreds and thousands
{{der-bottom}}

{{der-top}}
* {{ja-r|百%日|もも%か}}: [[hundredth]] [[day]]
* {{ja-r|百%声%鳥|もも%こえ%どり}}: ''[[Cuculus poliocephalus]]'', {{vern|lesser cuckoo}}
* {{ja-r|百舌|もず}}: [[shrike]]
* {{ja-r|百%千|もも%ち}}: a large number, all sorts, hundreds and thousands
* {{ja-r|百%千%鳥|もも%ち%どり}}: [[all sorts]] of [[bird]]s, hundreds and thousands of birds; a [[plover]]; a [[Japanese bush warbler]]
* {{ja-r|百%年|もも%とせ}}: hundred [[year]]s, [[century]], a long time
* {{ja-r|百%夜|もも%よ}}: a hundred [[night]]s
{{der-bottom}}

